{"word":"Eleazer","slug":"eleazer","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Eleazer</b> 1. Son of Aaron<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=6&verse=23'>Exo 6:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28&verse=1'>Exo 28:1</a> <br/> - Married a daughter of Putiel, who bore him Phinehas<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=6&verse=25'>Exo 6:25</a> <br/> - After the death of Nadab and Abihu is made chief of the tribe of Levi<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=3&verse=32'>Num 3:32</a> <br/> - Duties of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=4&verse=16'>Num 4:16</a> <br/> - Succeeds Aaron as high priest<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=20&verse=26'>Num 20:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=20&verse=28'>Num 20:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=10&verse=6'>Deu 10:6</a> <br/> - Assists Moses in the census<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=26&verse=63'>Num 26:63</a> <br/> - With Joshua, divides Palestine<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=34&verse=17'>Num 34:17</a> <br/> - Death and burial of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=24&verse=33'>Jos 24:33</a> <br/> - Descendants of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=24&verse=19'>1Ch 24:19</a> <br/> 2. An inhabitant of Kirjath-Jearim who attended the ark<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=7&verse=2'>1Sa 7:2</a><br/> 3. A Merarite Levite<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=23&verse=22'>1Ch 23:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=24&verse=28'>1Ch 24:28</a><br/> 4. Son of Dodo, and one of David's distinguished heroes<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=23&verse=10'>2Sa 23:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=23&verse=13'>2Sa 23:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=11&verse=12'>1Ch 11:12</a><br/> 5. Son of Phinehas<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=8&verse=33'>Ezr 8:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=42'>Neh 12:42</a><br/> 6. A returned Israelitish exile<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=10&verse=25'>Ezr 10:25</a>"}]}